    "## 3. Feature Extraction\n",
    "\n",
    "For each song I mix the 4 stems, take a random 10s crop, and extract:\n",
    "- **MFCC** (40 coefficients × mean+std = 80 features) — captures timbre\n",
    "- **Chroma** (12 × mean+std = 24) — captures pitch class distribution\n",
    "- **Spectral contrast** (7 × mean+std = 14) — captures spectral peaks vs valleys\n",
    "- **RMS energy** (mean+std = 2) — overall loudness\n",
    "- **Zero crossing rate** (mean+std = 2) — noisiness / percussion\n",
    "- **Spectral rolloff** (mean+std = 2) — brightness\n",
    "\n",
    "Total: **124 features per clip**"
   ]
  },
